  <info>
    <title>TextField - 文本输入框</title>

    <author>
      <personname>牛佳庆</personname>

      <email>njq.niu@hand-china.com</email>
    </author>
  </info>

  <para>文本输入框.输入框有只读,必输等状态.</para>

  <para>输入框可以绑定到某个DataSet上,通过设置DataSet的Field的一些属性来设置对应的输入框的状态.</para>

  <example>
    <title>代码示例</title>

    <programlisting role="xml">&lt;textField id="text4" required="true" prompt="输入框" emptyText="必须输入" width="150" /&gt;</programlisting>
  </example>

  <table class="pro_table">
    <caption>属性说明</caption>

    <thead>
      <tr>
        <td>属性名</td>

        <td>说明</td>
      </tr>
    </thead>

    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>id</td>

        <td>组件ID</td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td>bindTarget</td>

        <td>绑定的DataSet的id</td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td>name</td>

        <td>绑定到DataSet的Field的name</td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td>width</td>

        <td>宽度</td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td>prompt</td>

        <td>输入框的标签</td>
      </tr>
	  <tr>
        <td>emptyText</td>

        <td>提示信息</td>
      </tr>
	  <tr>
        <td>required</td>

        <td>是否必输</td>
      </tr>
	  <tr>
        <td>readonly</td>

        <td>是否只读</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</article>
